@startuml Sequence_Candidate_Dashboard
title Ứng Viên - Dashboard Cá Nhân (Module D)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant DashboardService as "Dashboard\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Xem Dashboard ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Dashboard"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show loading
FrontEnd -> DashboardService: GET /api/dashboard/candidate
DashboardService -> Database: Query user statistics
Database --> DashboardService: Stats data
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Dashboard data
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị dashboard

== Dashboard Content ==

DashboardService -> Database: Query user statistics
Database --> DashboardService: Stats data
DashboardService --> FrontEnd: Dashboard data

FrontEnd --> Candidate: Show stats & widgets

== Quick Actions ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Tìm việc"
FrontEnd --> FrontEnd: Navigate

@enduml
